  "3227240": {
    "name": "MineGeon: Renegades",
    "steam_appid": 3227240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/d6932cacc177b949d8b3d8e47e941b54.avif?t=1770399514\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MineGeon: Renegades</strong> 是一款以资源收集为核心的科幻类 roguelite 弹幕游戏。一次失败的抢劫行动后，一支名为“叛逆者”（Renegades）的队伍被迫逃亡，并在神秘的帕伊莫星附近坠毁。别无选择，他们只能深入星球的深处寻找帮助，却意外发现了本应永远被埋藏的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与朋友一同深入探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/b7beff38ac4f2d4892c1499b1084ebe9.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/b7beff38ac4f2d4892c1499b1084ebe9.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/b7beff38ac4f2d4892c1499b1084ebe9.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自一人，或与最多两名好友一起深入 PAIMO 的深处进行探索。协调彼此的行动、共享你的装备，团队合作是生存的关键。但也要小心……有时你必须释放内心的叛逆者，脱离队伍，才能最大化你的奖励。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>装备、武器与终极技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/51fecb79f555f25365cb35a1d316395e.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/51fecb79f555f25365cb35a1d316395e.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/51fecb79f555f25365cb35a1d316395e.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 MineGeon 内，你可以通过升级来解锁强大的装备，这些工具能够提供多种增益效果，帮助你在战斗中取得优势。你还可以从不同的终极技能中进行选择，这些特殊能力将决定你的玩法风格，并装备多种适合你策略的武器。将装备、武器与终极技能组合起来，会形成独特的协同效果，塑造你深入帕伊莫的冒险之旅。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集你的矿物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/670b10c8509265577867b8dc8916c845.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/670b10c8509265577867b8dc8916c845.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/670b10c8509265577867b8dc8916c845.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAIMO 遍布能激发你内心贪欲的矿物。你下降得越深，获得的奖励越丰厚，同时风险也越高。收集珍贵矿物并将它们兑换为永久升级，但请谨慎选择何时将它们送回你的飞船。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迎战强敌</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/114462fc8eb1fe75fdfc04f893be2217.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/114462fc8eb1fe75fdfc04f893be2217.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/114462fc8eb1fe75fdfc04f893be2217.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAIMO 的各个生态区栖息着种类繁多的敌人。在你的旅途中，你将遇到清道夫（Scavengers），他们不惜一切代价阻止你继续下潜。他们为何如此执着，不让你深入？每个生态区的终点都将迎来一场极限 Boss 战，全面考验你的技巧与策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级与进阶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/1acdebce981a0bb9d8275b00a29e9332.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/1acdebce981a0bb9d8275b00a29e9332.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/1acdebce981a0bb9d8275b00a29e9332.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 MineGeon: Renegades 中，进程是你生存与成功的关键。随着你不断探索并收集资源，你可以升级技能和装备，让自己在每一次冒险中变得更强。为你的飞船投资永久升级，并强化每位叛逆者的属性，以迎接前方的挑战</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的叛逆者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/77bcc84105ae2ce69aa75e4a9e935347.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/77bcc84105ae2ce69aa75e4a9e935347.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/77bcc84105ae2ce69aa75e4a9e935347.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在三种职业中进行选择，每种职业都拥有独特的终极技能和各自的属性。从坚韧的坦克 Marshall、致命的输出枪手 Trevor，到平衡型工程师 Ari，任你挑选。找到你在团队中的定位，并与其他叛逆者协同合作，最大化你在下潜 PAIMO 过程中生存的可能性。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/d706d1989d34465aec2b4f356bcbb274.poster.avif?t=1770399514\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/d706d1989d34465aec2b4f356bcbb274.webm?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227240/extras/d706d1989d34465aec2b4f356bcbb274.mp4?t=1770399514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在帕伊莫的深处，矗立着脉动着古老科技的神秘巨石。这些遗迹让叛逆者们可以决定接下来的下潜方向——你们可以作为一个团队投票，选择对所有人有利的道路，或是追随你自己的野心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好与你的朋友一起潜入深渊吧。开辟你的道路，聚集力量，并努力生存下去。你有足够的实力抵达 Pa⟊⧫⍜… 最深处吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将 <strong>MineGeon: Renegades</strong> 添加到愿望单，加入这场冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 简体中文, 韩语, 日语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 越南语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
